A. CLIENT INITIALIZATION

- LOCATION
        Sites hosting the clients.

- EXECUTING THE CLIENT SIDE

        i) setting the classpath

                JAVA_HOME=/opt/jdk-default/

        ii) set the flags

                PG_FLAGS=-EBclass Escada.tpc.tpcc.TPCCEmulation \
                         -KEY false \
                         -CLI 1 \
                         -Stclass Escada.tpc.tpcc.TPCCStateTransition \
                         -DBclass Escada.tpc.tpcc.database.postgresql.dbPostgresql \
                         -TRACEFLAG TRACE \
                         -PREFIX Cliente \
                         -DBpath jdbc:postgresql://192.168.82.183:5432/tpcc \
                         -DBdriver org.postgresql.Driver \
                         -DBusr tpcc \
                         -DBpasswd 123456 \
                         -POOL 0 \
                         -MI 45
			 -FRAG 1

        iii) run everything using the client startup class

                $(JVM) -cp $(classpath) -Xmx1024 Escada.tpc.common.clients.ClientStartup $(PG_FLAGS)

